{"id":131,"parent_id":124,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":131,"title":"Romans 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rom.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","The law of Moses is fulfilled in Christ—Paul delights in the law of God after the inward man."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.1","order":"03.08.007.15559"},["b","1"],"Know ye not, brethren, (for I speak to them that know the law,) how that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"law"],"hath dominion over a man as long as he liveth?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.2","order":"03.08.007.15560"},["b","2"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"woman"],"which hath an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"husband"],"is bound by the law to",["i","her"],"husband so long as he liveth; but if the husband be dead, she is loosed from the law of",["i","her"],"husband."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.3","order":"03.08.007.15561"},["b","3"],"So then if, while",["i","her"],"husband liveth, she be married to another man, she shall be called an adulteress: but if her husband be dead, she is free from that law; so that she is no adulteress, though she be married to another man."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.4","order":"03.08.007.15562"},["b","4"],"Wherefore, my brethren, ye also are become",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"dead"],"to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"law"],"by the body of Christ; that ye should be married to another,",["i","even"],"to him who is raised from the dead, that we should bring forth fruit unto God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.5","order":"03.08.007.15563"},["b","5"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"For"],"when we were in the flesh, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"motions of sins"],", which were by the law, did work in our members to bring forth fruit unto",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"death"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.6","order":"03.08.007.15564"},["b","6"],"But now we are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"delivered from"],"the law, that being",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"dead"],"wherein we were held; that we should serve in newness of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"spirit"],", and not",["i","in"],"the oldness of the letter."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.7","order":"03.08.007.15565"},["b","7"],"What shall we say then?",["i","Is"],"the law sin?",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"God forbid"],". Nay, I had not known sin, but by the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"law"],": for I had not known",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"lust"],", except the law had said, Thou shalt not",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.8","order":"03.08.007.15566"},["b","8"],"But sin, taking occasion by the commandment, wrought in me all manner of concupiscence. For without the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"law"],"sin",["i","was"],"dead."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.9","order":"03.08.007.15567"},["b","9"],"For I was alive without the law once: but when the commandment came, sin revived, and I died."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.10","order":"03.08.007.15568"},["b","10"],"And the commandment, which",["i","was ordained"],"to life, I found",["i","to be"],"unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"death"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.11","order":"03.08.007.15569"},["b","11"],"For sin,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"taking occasion"],"by the commandment, deceived me, and by it slew",["i","me."]],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.12","order":"03.08.007.15570"},["b","12"],"Wherefore the law",["i","is"],"holy, and the commandment holy, and just, and good."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.13","order":"03.08.007.15571"},["b","13"],"Was then that which is good made death unto me?",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"God forbid"],". But sin, that it might appear sin, working death in me by that which is good; that sin by the commandment might become exceeding sinful."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.14","order":"03.08.007.15572"},["b","14"],"For we know that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"law"],"is spiritual: but I am",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"carnal"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"sold under"],"sin."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.15","order":"03.08.007.15573"},["b","15"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"For"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"that which I do"],"I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"allow"],"not: for what I",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"would"],", that do I not; but what I hate, that do I."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.16","order":"03.08.007.15574"},["b","16"],"If then I do that which I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"would"],"not, I consent unto the law that",["i","it is"],"good."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.17","order":"03.08.007.15575"},["b","17"],"Now then it is no more I that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"do"],"it, but sin that dwelleth in me."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.18","order":"03.08.007.15576"},["b","18"],"For I know that in me (that is, in my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"flesh"],",)",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"dwelleth"],"no good thing: for to will is present with me; but",["i","how"],"to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"perform"],"that which is good I find not."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.19","order":"03.08.007.15577"},["b","19"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"good"],"that I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"would"],"I do not: but the evil which I would not, that I do."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.20","order":"03.08.007.15578"},["b","20"],"Now if I do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"that I would not"],", it is no more I that do it, but sin that dwelleth in me."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.21","order":"03.08.007.15579"},["b","21"],"I find then a law, that, when I would do good, evil is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"present"],"with me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.22","order":"03.08.007.15580"},["b","22"],"For I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"delight"],"in the law of God after the inward man:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.23","order":"03.08.007.15581"},["b","23"],"But I see another law in my members,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"warring"],"against the law of my mind, and bringing me into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"captivity"],"to the law of sin which is in my members."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.24","order":"03.08.007.15582"},["b","24"],"O",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"wretched"],"man that I am! who shall deliver me from the body of this death?"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.25","order":"03.08.007.15583"},["b","25"],"I thank God through Jesus Christ our Lord. So then with the mind I myself serve the law of God; but with the flesh the law of sin."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.1a","order":"03.08.007.15584"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.30.29-32"},"Mosiah 13:30 (29–32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.2a","order":"03.08.007.15586"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-wives"},"TG Marriage, Wives"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.2b","order":"03.08.007.15588"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-marry"},"TG Marriage, Marry"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.4a","order":"03.08.007.15590"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/2.19"},"Gal. 2:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.25.24-27"},"2 Ne. 25:25 (24–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/74.5.2-6"},"D&C 74:5 (2–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.4b","order":"03.08.007.15592"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/13.28.27-29"},"Mosiah 13:28 (27–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.5a","order":"03.08.007.15594"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/7.5-27"},["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 7:5–27 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.5b","order":"03.08.007.15596"},["b","5b"],["span.small","GR"],"sufferings, afflictions."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.5c","order":"03.08.007.15598"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.5.4-10"},"2 Ne. 2:5 (4–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.23"},"25:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.14.12-16"},"Alma 42:14 (12–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.6a","order":"03.08.007.15600"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"released, freed from."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.6b","order":"03.08.007.15602"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/5.17"},"2 Cor. 5:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.6c","order":"03.08.007.15604"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/2.29.28-29"},"Rom. 2:29 (28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.7a","order":"03.08.007.15606"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"May it not be!"],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.7b","order":"03.08.007.15608"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/82.3.3-4"},"D&C 82:3 (3–4)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.7c","order":"03.08.007.15610"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.7d","order":"03.08.007.15612"},["b","7d"],["span.small","GR"],"lust for, set the heart upon.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covet"},"TG Covet"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.8a","order":"03.08.007.15614"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/42.17.14-24"},"Alma 42:17 (14–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.10a","order":"03.08.007.15616"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/3.7"},"2 Cor. 3:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.11a","order":"03.08.007.15618"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"having taken opportunity."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.13a","order":"03.08.007.15620"},["b","13a"],["span.small","GR"],"May it not be!"],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.14a","order":"03.08.007.15622"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.34"},"D&C 29:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.14b","order":"03.08.007.15624"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/carnal-mind"},"TG Carnal Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.14c","order":"03.08.007.15626"},["b","14c"],["span.small","GR"],"devoted to, a slave to."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.15a","order":"03.08.007.15628"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rom/7.15-17"},["span.small","JST"],"Rom. 7:15–17 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.15b","order":"03.08.007.15630"},["b","15b"],["span.small","GR"],"what I produce, achieve."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.15c","order":"03.08.007.15632"},["b","15c"],["span.small","GR"],"know, understand."],["div",{"id":"15d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.15d","order":"03.08.007.15634"},["b","15d"],["span.small","GR"],"choose, intend, design."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.16a","order":"03.08.007.15636"},["b","16a"],["span.small","GR"],"choose, intend, design."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.17a","order":"03.08.007.15638"},["b","17a"],["span.small","GR"],"produce, work."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.18a","order":"03.08.007.15640"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"},"TG Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.18b","order":"03.08.007.15642"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/22.15"},"Alma 22:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.18c","order":"03.08.007.15644"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.19.17-20,26"},"2 Ne. 4:19 (17–20, 26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.19a","order":"03.08.007.15646"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/opposition"},"TG Opposition"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.19b","order":"03.08.007.15648"},["b","19b"],["span.small","GR"],"intend, choose."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.20a","order":"03.08.007.15650"},["b","20a"],["span.small","GR"],"what I do not intend, choose."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.21a","order":"03.08.007.15652"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.1"},"Heb. 12:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.18.17-19"},"2 Ne. 4:18 (17–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.22a","order":"03.08.007.15654"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirituality"},"TG Spirituality"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.23a","order":"03.08.007.15656"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/13.28"},"Alma 13:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.23b","order":"03.08.007.15658"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"TG Bondage, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rom/7.24a","order":"03.08.007.15660"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.17"},"2 Ne. 4:17"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"TG Sorrow"],"."]]}
